		('LOC_FEATURE_SUK_MONUMENTVALLEY_NAME',
		'Tsé Bii’ Ndzisgaii'),

		('LOC_FEATURE_SUK_MONUMENTVALLEY_DESCRIPTION',
		'Three tile impassable natural wonder. Provides +1 [ICON_Faith] Faith, +1 [ICON_Production] Production to adjacent tiles. Tiles of {LOC_FEATURE_SUK_MONUMENTVALLEY_NAME} that are part of a National Park also provide +2 [ICON_Gold] Gold to adjacent tiles, and give the owner +1 [ICON_Favor] Diplomatic Favor.'),
